{"tid":2172614,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"我知你有成日睇開呢度，淨係想問你.....你最近好嗎？","createTime":"2020-08-24T17:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T19:07:29.000Z","uid":260693,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"80b0755dc1a82288f5282023414ed225f3d5f17f","tid":2172614,"uid":260693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:24:33.000Z","msg":"雖然同你已經有兩年冇聯絡，但我唔知點解成日發夢見到你。當我夢醒既時候，我好想問你最近過成點，但我冇勇氣開口去問你，我怕打擾左你既生活。唯有係度問你，你最近好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n一位舊&rsquo;朋友&rsquo;字"},{"pid":"ff42cbfc6504c599b12bf059b2cebf5492368aee","tid":2172614,"uid":297436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:27:57.000Z","msg":"睇到都唔知係你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d9ffc804ce1c9cd98c1d82782cec58f4643850","tid":2172614,"uid":122798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:31:46.000Z","msg":"現實：好同唔好都唔關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66097476e19ab76be57340a81102e8320c69cc43","tid":2172614,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:34:56.000Z","msg":"走啦， 我唔想搞大佢"},{"pid":"94982b26002a5ecdca2f0c4eb7ad589aa92f959a","tid":2172614,"uid":10048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:39:01.000Z","msg":"其實想搵咪搵囉，俾啲勇氣啦"},{"pid":"9c8b5340b4f0ced3f3a6d7e2f33d33b5f7671938","tid":2172614,"uid":330051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:45:28.000Z","msg":"如果我話唔好你會唔會搵翻佢<br />\n<br />\n勿認真，純粹想叫你自己諗下究竟有咩意義"},{"pid":"377addef04eae1c783ae1b11fb88c84472d4c128","tid":2172614,"uid":260693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T18:55:23.000Z","msg":"多謝各位既意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係因為以我所認識既佢係一個好負面既人，而我曾經係佢既精神之柱，佢曾經又為過我放棄自我，愈諗愈擔心佢既狀況。先至好糾結搵唔搵佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p